        "subject": "LU-4653 fid: only compare non-IDIF seq in lu_fid_diff",
        "message": "LU-4653 fid: only compare non-IDIF seq in lu_fid_diff\n\nBecause it will pack OST index into IDIF FID in 2.6, and\nin 2.4/2.5, the OST index in IDIF FID is always 0. So we\nonly compare non-IDIF sequence in lu_fid_diff.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I15160d701db2dc9c211748e60d4fcc7bbb45af55\n"
      },
